    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255920/extras/accd38ced8b5803b3376e7c1c1331ff1.poster.avif?t=1728311986\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255920/extras/accd38ced8b5803b3376e7c1c1331ff1.webm?t=1728311986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255920/extras/accd38ced8b5803b3376e7c1c1331ff1.mp4?t=1728311986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>💫 <strong>FEATURES</strong> 💫<br>🧲 101 levels with unique gravity!<br>🧲 Real-world physics<br>🧲 Endless number of ways to complete levels<br>🧲 Various types of celestial bodies<br>🧲 Difficult and rewarding levels<br>🧲 Customization: colorful, rainbowy trails and trajectory indicators<br>🧲 Relaxing music and minimalistic graphics<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255920/extras/494cb777111379eeb0086ec17444946e.poster.avif?t=1728311986\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255920/extras/494cb777111379eeb0086ec17444946e.webm?t=1728311986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255920/extras/494cb777111379eeb0086ec17444946e.mp4?t=1728311986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>💫 <strong>SUMMARY</strong> 💫<br>You play as a comet bouncing around the galaxy; trying to get your lost kitty back. For reasons yet unknown the cat has left you fragments of the galaxy's map. Only collecting all the parts will lead you back to your kitty. To do so you have to learn how to manipulate gravity to your advantage whilst obeying the laws of nature. Exploit Newtonian mechanics to their limit!<br><br><strong>The kitty is waiting</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255920/extras/f6235d67b74a9e4af8d65036aad91805.poster.avif?t=1728311986\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255920/extras/f6235d67b74a9e4af8d65036aad91805.webm?t=1728311986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1255920/extras/f6235d67b74a9e4af8d65036aad91805.mp4?t=1728311986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
